{"tid":733392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美對中國加徵關稅 廠商可有90天申請豁免","createTime":"2018-07-07T16:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T04:11:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"c0fd2f19545f1f7bcbab440bfa62ab3a9cc0deb0","tid":733392,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T16:59:13.000Z","msg":"美對中國加徵關稅 廠商可有90天申請豁免<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B5%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E5%8F%AF%E6%9C%8990%E5%A4%A9%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D-151010905.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%25B0%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%258A%25A0%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E9%2597%259C%25E7%25A8%2585-%25E5%25BB%25A0%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258F%25AF%25E6%259C%258990%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E8%25B1%2581%25E5%2585%258D-151010905.html&d=0a7N8KJevEizjs8w0wV909r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5a5513cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%B0%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%8A%A0%E5%BE%B5%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85-%E5%BB%A0%E5%95%86%E5%8F%AF%E6%9C%8990%E5%A4%A9%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D-151010905.html</a><br />\n<br />\n（路透華盛頓6日電）美國貿易代表署（USTR）今天表示，在美國對進口中國商品加徵關稅中爭取豁免的公司，可有90天時間提出此一請求，迄10月9日為止。<br />\n<br />\n在美方對價值大約340億美元的中國商品開始課徵25%進口關稅僅數小時後，貿易代表署表示，所有申請通過的豁免待遇有效期限均為一年，且以7月6日為效期開始日。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表署說：「本署在對每一項豁免請求作出決定時，可能會考量一項產品是否能自中國以外來源取得；加徵的關稅是否會對申請方或其他美國利益造成嚴重經濟損害；同時特定產品是否具有戰略重要性，或是否與『中國製造2025』等中國產業計畫有關。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://一旦提出申請並張貼在www.regulations.gov\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A6%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E4%B8%A6%E5%BC%B5%E8%B2%BC%E5%9C%A8www.regulations.gov&d=0a7N8KJevEizjs8w0wV909r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=c3085e15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">一旦提出申請並張貼在www.regulations.gov</a>網站後，將有14天時間蒐集輿情，此後還有7天時間可予以反駁。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n貿易代表署說：「由於豁免權是針對產品，因此同一產品的進口可一體適用，而無論進口商是否曾提出申請。」</span>中央社(翻譯)"},{"pid":"37a307b9b48708c685fedfa89e6073518697af21","tid":733392,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"老美龜縮"},{"pid":"4b303dbaca01974377d80f54d89ddf916a4d1cd8","tid":733392,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:05:57.000Z","msg":"侵侵呢招仆街到絕<br />\n過哂d 有毒既親中公司<br />\n<br />\n然後中國就斷尻班奸商財路<br />\n好似大豆先生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c03b4d90505684937ba5e09136703f3e7baeda5","tid":733392,"uid":43173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:12:16.000Z","msg":"係時候考驗中国商人有幾爱国<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dae80c57b4d5bb14be75a5fad2c4a8a1bcf48bb","tid":733392,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:26:16.000Z","msg":"又玩乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b6f20f95a10645a17a9f2597623b488fb55ac1f","tid":733392,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-07T17:50:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>侵侵呢招仆街到絕<br />\n過哂d 有毒既親中公司<br />\n<br />\n然後中國就斷尻班奸商財路<br />\n好似大豆先生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[img]assets/faces/dog/smile.gif[/img] [img]assets/faces/dog/smile.gif[/img] [img]assets/faces/dog/smile.gif[/img]</blockquote><br />\n咁都可以幫特朗普兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm